OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with the odd spot
OL,7,Fof rain possible at first. Cloud
OL,8,Fthickening overnight with more
OL,9,Fpersistent and heavy rain likely,
OL,10,Fparticularly in western parts. Rather
OL,11,Fbreezy especially along coasts. Mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA grey and often wet start
OL,14,Fto the day across Wales, particularly
OL,15,Ffurther north. However, rain will
OL,16,Fgradually ease, with some drier and
OL,17,Fpossibly brighter warm spells in the
OL,18,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
